				</a>
			</h2>
			<div class='social-icons flex items-start'>
				<a class='p-3 dark:hidden' href='mailto:li002843@umn.edu' target='_blank'>
					<Image src={EnvelopeBlack} width={SocialIconSize} height={SocialIconSize} alt='Email icon' loading="eager" />
				</a>
				<a class='p-3 hidden dark:block' href='mailto:li002843@umn.edu' target='_blank'>
					<Image src={EnvelopeWhite} width={SocialIconSize} height={SocialIconSize} alt='Email icon' loading="eager" />
				</a>
				<!-- <a class='p-3 dark:hidden' href='https://github.com/eigenan' target='_blank'>
					<Image src={GithubBlack} width={SocialIconSize} height={SocialIconSize} alt='Github logo' loading="eager" />
				</a>
				<a class='p-3 hidden dark:block' href='https://github.com/eigenan' target='_blank'>
					<Image src={GithubWhite} width={SocialIconSize} height={SocialIconSize} alt='Github logo' loading="eager" />
				</a> -->
